| Best Practice                           | Summary                                         |
| --------------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| ğŸ”’ Lock the root user                   | Protect with MFA, donâ€™t share it                |
| ğŸ” Least privilege principle            | Only give needed permissions                    |
| ğŸ‘¥ Use roles instead of long-term users | Temporary and safer credentials                 |
| ğŸŒ Use Identity Providers               | Centralized identity management                 |
| ğŸ¢ IAM Identity Center                  | Enterprise-level identity and access management |
